      <h2>Css - DataTable</h2>
      <p>Created to facilitate interaction with the management of your application tables. Needing only a table in html
        to be instantiated automatically. Uses javascript for its creation, as you can check in JS
        (<%= link_to :link, js_datatable_path %>).</p>


